{
  "stem": "11205.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must-- probably he felt the vibration or something, because we didn't know, and he said-- he start to move away, to crawl away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, they're coming, they're coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I looked up, I start to count.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was maybe 20 airplanes, and I saw the bombs falling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But for me, I-- I couldn't understand what it is-- what happened just across the road.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A bomb fell into a building and was killed-- four people were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and then we start to run to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the cellar, we were about 30 people in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when it was already over, we came-- I came-- it was already evening, and I came out to-- to-- to the front of the street, and I saw this house burning, and people was start-- with water-- buckets of water to hand over.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I got-- it hit me then, and I got so hysteric, and I started to run to-- my sister who lived on the other part of the city.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I came there, I don't know how this happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My parents were already there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't even know how it happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I came in there, and I found it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that-- that was the first-- the eighth day of-- of-- that we start to feel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Later on, when we-- my parents collect all the children, and we left town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We walked-- we went where I was on-- on this holiday about-- I-- I don't know how many miles, about 10 miles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A whole night, we walked, and we came there because we didn't want to see-- to be in the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was before Yontif.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother prepared all of the foods.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
